## UI Design System — follow these rules on every component, page, and edit

### Colors
--color-brand: #635bff;
--color-brand-hover: #5146e8;
--color-brand-light: #f0effe;
--color-bg: #f6f9fc;
--color-surface: #ffffff;
--color-border: #e0e6ed;
--color-text-primary: #0a2540;
--color-text-muted: #8898aa;
--color-success: #3ecf8e;
--color-danger: #fa755a;

### Typography
- Font: system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif
- Page title: 20px / 600 weight
- Body: 14px / 400 weight
- Labels/meta: 11–12px uppercase, letter-spacing 0.07em, muted color

### Layout & shape
- Border radius: 6px components, 10px cards
- Border: 1px solid #e0e6ed
- Card padding: 16–20px
- Page background: #f6f9fc, surface/card background: #ffffff

### Sidenav
- Width 220px, white bg, right border
- Active item: #f0effe bg + 3px left border in brand color + brand text
- Hover: #f6f9fc bg

### Buttons
- Primary: brand bg, white text, 8px 16px padding, 6px radius, hover darken
- Active press: scale(0.97)
- Transition: all 0.15s ease

### Cards
- White bg, 1px border, 10px radius
- Hover: box-shadow 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.07)

### Status badges
- Success: bg #eafaf3, text #1b8a5a
- Pending: bg #fff8e6, text #b07d00
- Failed: bg #fff0ee, text #c0392b
- Shape: 3px 10px padding, 20px border-radius

### Motion
- Entrance: opacity 0→1 + translateY(10px)→0, staggered 80ms per element
- All transitions: 0.15s ease

### Rules — never break these
- No gradients, no heavy shadows, no blurs anywhere
- Flat white cards on light gray page background
- One primary CTA button per view, secondary actions as text links in brand color
- Text links: brand color, font-weight 500, append " →" for navigation
- Data tables: 11px uppercase muted headers, row hover tinted bg, amounts in font-weight 600

## Consistency rule
When editing an existing page, always match the existing component patterns exactly.
When adding a new page or component, refer back to this file before writing any styles.
Never introduce a new color, font size, or spacing value not listed here.